Direxion Daily AAPL Bull 2X Shares (NASDAQ:AAPU) Short Interest Down 58.8% in March
results.description: Direxion Daily AAPL Bull 2X Shares (NASDAQ:AAPU - Get Free Report) was the recipient of a significant decline in short interest during the month of March. As of March 31st, there was short interest totalling 255,600 shares, a decline of 58.8% from the March 15th total of 620,300 shares. Based on an average trading volume of 1,483,300 shares, the short-interest ratio is currently 0.2 days. Currently, 7.4% of the shares of the stock are short sold.
